("resolv: Remove support for RES_USE_INET6 and the inet6 option").

Reviewed-by: Siddhesh Poyarekar <siddhesh@sourceware.org>
(cherry picked from commit a7fc30b522a0cd7c8c5e7e285b9531b704e02f04)
